Allright, nevermind. After two years at this school, it seems I still 
havn't gotten hold of a valid scedule..

::Zardus::

Zardus nods. "State of the art Predacon technology."

They enter the bridge. Zardus looks at the scanner reports to see a 
battle. He smiles. Soon there would be one less faction contesting 
against the Alliance for supreme power.
